eu.cqse.check.framework.typetracker

Class ScopedTypeLookup

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.cqse.check.framework.typetracker.ScopedTypeLookup

  • public class ScopedTypeLookup
extends Object
    A scoped type lookup is an associative data structure that maps variable names to their type information. A scoped type lookup can create child lookups, that can shadow variables from the parent. Further imported namespaces are stored.
    Version:
    $Rev: 52958 $
    Author:
    $Author: hummelb $
